    "body": "Have you started geth? If so, could you provide your starting parameters?\r\nThe `geth.ipc` is usually located in `.ethereum/geth.ipc` or `/tmp/geth.ipc`\r\nThe startup log also prints out the location btw. \r\n```\r\n> geth --dev\r\nINFO [05-10|11:51:02.967] Starting Geth in ephemeral dev mode... \r\nINFO [05-10|11:51:02.969] Maximum peer count                       ETH=50 LES=0 total=50\r\nINFO [05-10|11:51:02.969] Smartcard socket not found, disabling    err=\"stat /run/pcscd/pcscd.comm: no such file or directory\"\r\nINFO [05-10|11:51:02.969] Set global gas cap                       cap=25000000\r\n[...]\r\nINFO [05-10|11:51:05.159] IPC endpoint opened                      url=/tmp/geth.ipc\r\nINFO [05-10|11:51:05.159] Transaction pool price threshold updated price=1000000000\r\nINFO [05-10|11:51:05.159] Transaction pool price threshold updated price=1\r\n```",
